        "content": "Web search results for query: \"GitHub Copilot updates February 2026 changelog release notes\"\n\nI'll search for GitHub Copilot updates from February 2026 to find changelog and release notes information.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"GitHub Copilot将支持来自Anthropic、Google和OpenAI的模型\",\"url\":\"https://m.163.com/dy/article/JFN9GJMQ0511BLFD.html\"},{\"title\":\"windiscover\",\"url\":\"https://windiscover.com/\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub召开全球开发者大会！20000处产品改进，Copilot重磅更新\",\"url\":\"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/318127278511130644.html\"},{\"title\":\"Visual Studio Code （v1.103） 中GitHub Copilot 最新更新！\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7536129770733846578\"},{\"title\":\"Microsoft 开发人员更改日志\",\"url\":\"https://developer.microsoft.com/zh-cn/changelog\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://apps.apple.com/mo/app/github/id1477376905?l=zh-Hant-TW?l=zh-tw\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://apps.apple.com/mo/app/github/id1477376905\"},{\"title\":\"Visual Studio Code （v1.103） 中 GitHub Copilot 最新更新！\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/angotech/article/details/150118536\"},{\"title\":\"祖传“屎山代码”终于有解了，GitHub Copilot Chat 下个月全面上线，聊聊天就能看懂代码、捉Bug！...\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/emprere/article/details/134522071\"},{\"title\":\"January 2024 (version 1.86)\",\"url\":\"https://code.visualstudio.com/updates/v1_86\"}]\n\nBased on my search for \"GitHub Copilot updates February 2026 changelog release notes,\" here are the key findings:\n\n## Search Results Summary\n\nUnfortunately, I couldn't find a specific, comprehensive changelog for GitHub Copilot updates from February 2026. The search results include some relevant information, but they are either from different time periods or don't provide detailed release notes for that specific timeframe. However, here's what I found:\n\n---\n\n### Microsoft Developer Changelog (Official Source)\nThe most relevant result is the **Microsoft Developer Changelog** which appears to contain recent GitHub updates, including:\n- **February 17, 2026**: Deprecation of selected Anthropic and OpenAI models across GitHub Copilot experiences\n- Copilot coding agent updates\n- Visual Studio agent improvements\n- Workflow dispatch API updates\n\n**Link**: [Microsoft Developer Changelog](https://developer.microsoft.com/zh-cn/changelog)\n\n---\n\n### GitHub Mobile App Updates (February 2026)\nAccording to the iOS App Store changelog:\n- **Version 1.245.0 (February 11, 2026)**: Added model selection when using Copilot Coding Agent\n- **Version 1.244.1 (February 4, 2026)**: Introduced Coding Agent Live Notifications to track coding session progress in real-time\n- **Version 1.244.0 (February 3, 2026)**: Bug fixes and improvements\n\n---\n\n### Other Related Updates (Various Sources)\n- **GitHub Copilot Model Integration**: Integration of Anthropic's Claude Sonnet 4.6 model was mentioned, though this appears to be from early February 2026\n- **Visual Studio Code Updates**: Version 1.103 brought improvements to chat workflows, agent tool selection, and terminal integration\n\n---\n\n### Recommendation\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date February 2026 release notes, I recommend checking:\n1. [The Official GitHub Blog](https://github.blog)\n2. [Microsoft Developer Changelog](https://developer.microsoft.com/changelog)\n3. [GitHub Copilot documentation](https://docs.github.com/copilot)\n\nWould you like me to search for more specific aspects of GitHub Copilot's February 2026 updates, or help you find information about particular features?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
