        "content": "Web search results for query: \"Windsurf Codeium updates February 2026 changelog new features\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave4版本发布，新增预览功能、支持指哪改哪\",\"url\":\"http://www.citnews.com.cn/news/202503/195711.html\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave 4版本发布，新增预览功能、支持指哪改哪\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1825901017149709058\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave2 大更新来了！让你瞬间拥有超强编程能力！\",\"url\":\"https://openi.cn/296822.html\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf Wave 6 更新：一键部署应用，还有智能提交、记忆增强等\",\"url\":\"https://www.douyin.com/discover?xigua_webid=7496046253017695759\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 新版发布，更新 Tab 体验\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7483033687954636851\"},{\"title\":\"软媒IT之家旗下站点\",\"url\":\"https://wap.ithome.com/soft/\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 推出全新品牌标志与功能，AI编码工具进一步优化\",\"url\":\"https://m.chinaz.com/ainews/17643.shtml\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 已升级其免费层级，提供更多积分、高级功能和新标志\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7498297126268354569\"},{\"title\":\"OpenAI in Talks to Acquire AI Coding Tool Windsurf for $3 Billion\",\"url\":\"https://m.sohu.com/a/886307984_122342248/?pvid=000115_3w_a\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 编辑器六大更新支持一键部署功能\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7488714182935691302\"}]\n\nBased on my search results, I found several updates about Windsurf (formerly Codeium), but **no specific changelog for February 2026** is currently available. Here's what I found:\n\n## Most Recent Update Available:\n**Wave 13 Version** (December 2025 - referenced in February 2026 coverage)\n- Major upgrades to multi-agent workflows\n- Performance and accessibility improvements\n- Enhanced terminal reliability\n- Further establishes Windsurf as a leading AI code editor\n\n## Recent Major Updates (2025):\n\n### Wave 6 Update (April 2025):\n- **One-click deployment** functionality\n- **Smart commit** features\n- Enhanced **memory and retrieval** capabilities\n- **Conversation directory** for better chat organization\n- Netlify integration support\n\n### Wave 4 Update (March 2025):\n- **Preview functionality** - see code changes in real-time\n- **Tab to Import** - simplified dependency management\n- **Cascade assistant** - intelligent suggestions for next steps\n- **Linter integration** - real-time code quality checking\n- New referral program introduced\n\n### Brand Changes (April 2025):\n- **New brand identity** and logo with wave and \"W\" elements\n- **Free tier upgraded** from 5 to 25 prompt credits monthly\n- Unlimited fast tab completions for free users\n- Unlimited preview access and daily deployment allowance\n- Cascade Base model available in \"writing\" mode\n\n### Tab Experience Enhancements:\n- Unified Autocomplete, Supercomplete, Tab to Jump, and Tab to Import\n- Improved context awareness using recent files, terminal commands, clipboard, and chat history\n- Enhanced code completion quality and speed\n- Green highlighting for accepted completions\n\n---\n\n**Note**: Since the current date is January 2025, any February 2026 information would be speculative or future-predicted content. The search results show actual updates through December 2025 (Wave 13). I recommend checking the [official Windsurf blog](https://codeium.com/blog) for the most current changelog information.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
